"Forced OFF by the AGNOSIS_DEBUG constant in wp-config.php — the checkbox "
"above has no effect until that line is removed."
msgstr ""
"Forzato su OFF dalla costante AGNOSIS_DEBUG in wp-config.php — la casella "
"sopra non ha effetto finché quella riga non viene rimossa."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1207
msgid "Directory"
msgstr "Directory"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1210
msgid "Filter with agnosis_debug_dir to redirect debug output elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Filtra con agnosis_debug_dir per reindirizzare altrove l’output di debug."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1217
msgid ".txt file(s) in the directory"
msgstr "file .txt nella directory"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1223
msgid ""
"Delete all .txt files in the debug directory? The directory itself stays in "
"place so future debug writes still land cleanly."
msgstr ""
"Eliminare tutti i file .txt nella directory di debug? La directory stessa "
"rimane in posizione, così le future scritture di debug continueranno a "
"essere salvate correttamente."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1228
msgid "Clear Debug Files"
msgstr "Cancella file di debug"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1260
msgid "Pipeline Logs"
msgstr "Log della pipeline"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1265
msgid "Clear all log entries?"
msgstr "Cancellare tutte le voci del registro?"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1266
msgid "Clear All"
msgstr "Cancella tutto"

#. translators: %d: total log entry count
#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1275
#, php-format
msgid ""
"%d entries total. Logs are pruned automatically according to the Inbox "
"retention setting."
msgstr ""
"%d voci totali. I log vengono eliminati automaticamente in base "
"all'impostazione di conservazione della posta in arrivo."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1282
msgid "No log entries yet."
msgstr "Non ci sono ancora voci di log."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1287
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Ora"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:1288
